### **Table: Current Manual CRM User Actions**

| Step | Human Action                                 | Who Performs It |
| ---- | -------------------------------------------- | --------------- |
| 1    | Open Order Status                            | CSR / Agent     |
| 2    | Read the Hold Reason                         | CSR / Agent     |
