# ğŸ¤– **2. How Accredo Lens Automates Each Human Step**

Accredo Lens integrates our **Order Agent**, **RAG orchestration**, and **credoservices APIs** to replace every human action programmatically.

### **Table: Human Action â†’ AI/Order Agent Automation**

| Manual Step              | AI Replacement                                  | Notes                                       |
| ------------------------ | ----------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------- |
| Open Order Status        | Order Agent fetches order, hold, SLA metadata   | Triggered by patient/prescriber interaction |
| Read Hold Reason         | Agent interprets hold + PA + DV + ENC data      | Summaries shown to user conversationally    |
| Click Escalate           | Agent auto-evaluates if escalation is allowed   | Follows exact business rules                |
| Tick checkboxes          | Agent verifies required checks using APIs       | No human confirmation needed                |
| Select escalation reason | Agent chooses correct reason based on rules     | Zero manual decisioning                     |
| Add a note               | Agent generates structured escalation note      | Captures context + patient intent           |
| Submit escalation        | Agent performs FLO case creation via API        | No UI interaction                           |
| Release from Hold        | Agent checks release rules, executes release    | Prevents invalid releases                   |
| Work escalation case     | Agent routes case to correct queue              | No inconsistent routing                     |
| Pharmacist review        | Agent flags when pharmacist review is mandatory | Optional: notify clinical queue             |

